right corner.",[17,275,276],{},[69,277],{"alt":71,"src":278},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F0ejHWw6.png",[17,280,281],{},"If I close the browser while reading \"NexT's useful features\", next time I click the bookmark and it sends me back to that article.",[17,283,284],{},[69,285],{"alt":71,"src":286},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FhAka1xQ.png",[12,288,290],{"id":289},"enable-article-sharing","Enable article sharing",[17,292,293],{},"Note: this feature was removed and moved to a plugin in around NexT 7.2.0.",[17,295,296],{},"Useful feature, off by default. Once enabled, every article gets share buttons at the bottom, and you can customise which ones appear.",[17,298,299],{},[69,300],{"alt":71,"src":301},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FbVOvbGt.png",[17,303,304,305,307,308,311,312,86,314,316,317,320],{},"Search ",[27,306,136],{}," for ",[27,309,310],{},"Likely Share"," and set ",[27,313,85],{},[27,315,112],{},". You can customise the share button names; to hide a button, just add ",[27,318,319],{},"#"," in front.",[17,322,323],{},[69,324],{"alt":71,"src":325},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F0juov0P.png",[12,327,329],{"id":328},"built-in-tags","Built-in tags",[17,331,332],{},"Too many settings to cover here — direct link instead (I don't use these much):",[17,334,335],{},[208,336,339],{"href":337,"rel":338},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.yangshixian.me\u002Fpost\u002F177574ba.html",[212],"NexT theme built-in styles (Chinese)",[12,341,343],{"id":342},"animation-settings","Animation settings",[17,345,346,347,113],{},"Most animation settings are here — search for ",[27,348,349],{},"motion",[17,351,352],{},[69,353],{"alt":71,"src":354},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FjTXSdyz.png",[17,356,357],{},"(Inner voice: honestly I prefer the defaults...)",[12,359,361],{"id":360},"lightbox-effect","Lightbox effect",[17,363,364,365,227],{},"NexT can do lightbox effects too. ",[27,366,226],{},[17,368,369],{},[69,370],{"alt":71,"src":232},[17,372,235],{},[237,374,376],{"cl